Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.40,0:01:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來雨快停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.40,0:01:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了 我還在擔心雨停不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.91,0:01:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就再等一會兒吧 直到雨停為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.71,0:01:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.48,0:01:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黃金假期也結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.38,0:01:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.58,0:01:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一放完假就要期中考了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.65,0:01:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過在這之前要先選學生會會長啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.46,0:01:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竹井會長說務必要請你接任下一屆的會長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.73,0:02:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然還是不想當吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.17,0:02:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 那個人…其他人也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.84,0:02:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道他在期待些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.31,0:02:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然會錯意了 我實在很困擾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.75,0:02:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實真正的我是更…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.05,0:02:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.62,0:02:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.75,0:02:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.06,0:02:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.00,0:02:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.43,0:02:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是潑春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.43,0:02:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潑春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.27,0:02:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雨這麼大你在這裡幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.70,0:02:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這句話應該我說才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.74,0:02:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全身都淋濕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.24,0:02:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會又迷路了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.84,0:02:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我在找東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.78,0:02:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.98,0:02:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在找這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.68,0:02:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇！真是可愛的小貓咪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.32,0:02:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道她會這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.62,0:02:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 她是老虎喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.16,0:02:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 老虎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.73,0:03:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩杞紗 是隻老虎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.76,0:03:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.63,0:03:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說老虎就是十二生肖的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.30,0:03:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十二生肖的老虎嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.67,0:03:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 我叫本田透…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.87,0:03:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.57,0:03:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.75,0:03:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 被咬了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.28,0:03:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.72,0:03:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杞紗 好好跟小透道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杞紗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.69,0:03:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.56,0:03:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希 小紗不會說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.46,0:03:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不會說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.27,0:03:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上國中後沒多久就突然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.01,0:03:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥說她是得了心病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.58,0:03:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不願意把話說出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.21,0:03:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從此就再也沒說過話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.98,0:03:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變成逃學的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.39,0:04:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天終於…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.99,0:04:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翹家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.66,0:04:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我四處找她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.83,0:04:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到時 已經變成一隻老虎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.07,0:04:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為被異性碰到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.50,0:04:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 好像只是身體太虛弱的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.34,0:04:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是為了什麼原因才變成這樣的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.28,0:04:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被欺負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.09,0:04:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊 怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.76,0:04:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳生氣了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.19,0:04:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪我多嘴是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.90,0:04:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.10,0:04:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要搞清楚 我們有多擔心妳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.80,0:04:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳爸媽現在正四處在找妳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.34,0:04:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.04,0:04:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 潑春你流血了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.38,0:04:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.08,0:05:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下落不明的杞紗…止血…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.88,0:05:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 妳冷靜點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.52,0:05:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我去幫杞紗止血…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.02,0:05:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳冷靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.89,0:05:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是紫吳你過度冷靜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.12,0:05:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潑春 你剛剛是不是"變黑"了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.79,0:05:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 就算很痛也只能生悶氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.10,0:05:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杞紗那傢伙真拿她沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.15,0:05:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杞紗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.38,0:05:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杞紗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.52,0:05:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杞紗 妳在這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.22,0:05:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 妳在這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.66,0:05:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…不痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.83,0:05:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不痛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.70,0:05:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是一點也不痛…對…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.17,0:05:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是有點痛又有點不痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.20,0:06:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之我們先回家吧 杞紗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.17,0:06:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杞紗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.64,0:06:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杞紗 我是媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.68,0:06:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是紫吳專程打電話給媽媽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.92,0:06:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.03,0:06:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老給周遭的人添麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.36,0:06:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底在幹什麼 到底在想什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.23,0:06:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓媽媽感到困擾真的這麼有趣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.97,0:06:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於擁有被怪物附身小孩的母親們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.84,0:06:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是過度保護孩子就是排斥他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.72,0:06:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳為何不說在學校被欺負了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.02,0:06:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何要離家出走呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.49,0:06:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何什麼都不說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.10,0:07:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.13,0:07:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.54,0:07:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她可能是說不出口吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.74,0:07:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一想到媽媽知道真相後會有什麼反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.98,0:07:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會很不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.08,0:07:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.65,0:07:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.62,0:07:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想讓人知道這樣的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.00,0:07:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拼命虛張聲勢想掩飾這一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.97,0:07:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.01,0:07:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.91,0:07:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓自己更覺得沒出息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.51,0:07:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更覺得丟臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.72,0:07:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定媽媽也很討厭這個被人欺負的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.53,0:08:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個人不斷在想這個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.17,0:08:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷想這個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.70,0:08:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以更是說不出口吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.81,0:08:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最擔心害怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.58,0:08:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最難過的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.42,0:08:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是被自己最喜歡的人討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.27,0:09:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寄住？你說杞紗嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.34,0:09:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為種種原因 暫時把她接來這裡住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.84,0:09:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼種種原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.98,0:09:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就別追問了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.51,0:09:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看她媽媽也快不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.65,0:09:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就當作是在復建吧 先讓她們暫時分開一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.62,0:09:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽得霧煞煞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.99,0:09:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杞紗到底跑哪兒去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.86,0:09:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緊黏著小透不放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.62,0:10:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杞紗寄住在這裡 經過了三天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.70,0:10:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.36,0:10:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說真的連上廁所都等 我實在覺得不好意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.24,0:10:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.14,0:10:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令人感到不可思議的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.51,0:10:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這三天裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.44,0:10:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杞紗對我是寸步不離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.69,0:10:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換句話說 就是她還蠻喜歡我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.69,0:10:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點像剛在學走路的小女娃 感覺挺溫馨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.16,0:10:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會覺得厭煩嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.26,0:10:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會嫌煩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.03,0:10:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的是…超愛妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.54,0:10:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她好像很開心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.14,0:10:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我實在搞不懂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.08,0:11:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.12,0:11:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我馬上做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.75,0:11:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杞紗 妳今晚想吃什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.96,0:11:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杞紗 妳連自己想吃什麼都不會說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.23,0:11:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨～\N喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.67,0:11:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於這個既笨又蠢的阿夾所說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.94,0:11:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳就別放在心上吧 小紗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.84,0:11:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別爬到我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.24,0:11:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別摸我 真噁心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.54,0:11:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.64,0:11:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.25,0:11:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杞紗 還是不願意開口說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.02,0:11:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我想到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.12,0:11:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走迷宮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.36,0:11:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.56,0:11:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 用走迷宮來決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.29,0:11:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 杞紗妳喜歡走哪條路線呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.33,0:12:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一條嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.84,0:12:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我要開始了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.21,0:12:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼歌呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.01,0:12:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.08,0:12:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚要吃韭菜蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.15,0:12:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虧妳說得出口 妳真是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.72,0:12:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？啊！我不是那個意思…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.75,0:12:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這該怎說好呢 那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.62,0:12:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳就給我用心點煮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.16,0:12:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.93,0:12:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭 為了這麼點小事拌嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.97,0:12:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.10,0:12:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什麼叫拌嘴嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.47,0:12:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杞紗遲早一定能用她那可愛的聲音跟我說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.08,0:12:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 也不能老住在紫吳家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.58,0:12:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杞紗今後該如何是好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.68,0:12:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是想這種問題的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.42,0:12:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她的個性認真 常想些不該想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.39,0:13:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會把自己逼到那種窘境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.63,0:13:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有她媽媽也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.67,0:13:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杞紗的媽媽已經沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.60,0:13:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她昨天打電話來道謝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.87,0:13:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.64,0:13:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杞紗她還好嗎 三餐都有吃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.11,0:13:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杞紗不喜歡乾乾的東西 她愛吃韭菜蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.52,0:13:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…那是杞紗的媽媽還是很愛杞紗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.69,0:13:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說的沒錯吧 否則根本不會打電話來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.30,0:13:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.20,0:13:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說的沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.53,0:13:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來 杞紗為何會被欺負呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.31,0:13:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.77,0:13:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.34,0:13:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我聽到伯母們的談話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.21,0:13:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為杞紗絕不肯告訴我原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.25,0:14:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 剛開始呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.45,0:14:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是外表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.52,0:14:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都說看不順眼她的頭髮跟眼睛顏色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.76,0:14:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛色不同的怪傢伙被排斥是她的宿命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.80,0:14:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是被說得很難聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.07,0:14:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說你的人不是都被你K得很慘嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.28,0:14:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比阿夾好一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.44,0:14:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙把人打得剩下半條命呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.05,0:14:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.25,0:14:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢 杞紗也盡了努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.92,0:14:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她告訴大家這個毛色是天生的她也沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.52,0:14:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果大家開始對她視而不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家不僅對她視而不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.13,0:14:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每當杞紗一說什麼大家就嘲笑她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.00,0:14:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說會竊竊地嘲笑她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.11,0:15:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 在我班上從沒人對我這樣過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.88,0:15:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我只能憑空想像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.58,0:15:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想像過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.62,0:15:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每當我說話時 大家都會在一旁竊笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.29,0:15:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那會是什麼樣的感覺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.79,0:15:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.83,0:15:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是非常…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.40,0:15:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悲哀的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被嘲笑的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.97,0:15:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後會變得愈來愈懦弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.54,0:15:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變得什麼話都不敢說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.48,0:15:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算明知周圍的人會很著急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.79,0:15:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是眼前卻是一片黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.96,0:15:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸愈來愈困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.73,0:15:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,內心也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.03,0:15:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,語言就這麼死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要上課了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.20,0:16:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希 我今天要去紫吳老師那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.74,0:16:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,順便有東西要給她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.68,0:16:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有東西給她？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.28,0:16:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信 杞紗的導師寄來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.15,0:16:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,內容可能讓人看了會想吐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.19,0:16:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不覺得變軟弱是件好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不覺得堅強就是好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.93,0:16:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說這是個弱肉強食的社會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.47,0:16:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們並非動物 我們是人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.74,0:16:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身為十二生肖的我們也是人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.88,0:16:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寫了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.01,0:17:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩同學 近況可好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.71,0:17:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該來學校了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.25,0:17:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,班上的同學們也都在等草摩同學來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.89,0:17:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有任何問題可以找老師商量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.66,0:17:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望妳能積極的加入這個團體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.26,0:17:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來就會發現最重要的事就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.13,0:17:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩同學必須先學著喜歡自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.13,0:17:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找出自己的優點 喜歡上自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.17,0:17:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳想想 連自己都討厭自己 別人又怎麼會喜歡妳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.82,0:17:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是超噁心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.09,0:18:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫做喜歡自己呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.53,0:18:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己的優點該從何找起呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.73,0:18:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只知道自己的缺點是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.77,0:18:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因為不知道才討厭自己的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.27,0:18:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.48,0:18:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.58,0:18:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該不是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.68,0:18:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當有人說喜歡自己時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.22,0:18:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是自己開始喜歡上自己的時候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.99,0:18:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當有人肯接納自己時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.56,0:18:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得自己也就能開始原諒及喜歡自己了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.11,0:18:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杞紗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.72,0:19:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都非常喜歡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.79,0:19:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…也只能這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.33,0:19:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們能做的只有喜歡妳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.21,0:19:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.12,0:19:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒聽到妳的聲音了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.57,0:19:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.30,0:19:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.61,0:19:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杞紗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.04,0:19:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杞紗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.75,0:20:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.22,0:20:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起話雖然還有點結巴的杞紗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.69,0:20:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然說要去上學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.53,0:20:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實說 對於杞紗的離開 我還真是有點不捨呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.88,0:20:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果繼續這麼下去 情況可能會更糟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.38,0:20:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算不能跟大家合好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.52,0:20:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續被大家無視於我的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.13,0:20:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也會忍耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.39,0:20:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杞紗正打算鼓起勇氣勇於面對問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.73,0:20:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希也一起來就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.04,0:21:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說還有重要的事要辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.74,0:21:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.14,0:21:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉 我至今不斷的逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.21,0:21:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,造成你莫大的困擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.01,0:21:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我當上會長 我會全力以赴盡到會長職責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.82,0:21:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好彌補之前的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.72,0:21:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.35,0:21:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還請你多多的指導我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.92,0:21:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是為了我才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.13,0:21:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}斬\N釘\N截\N鐵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.13,0:21:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.37,0:21:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.64,0:21:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然變堅強了 也沒有改變什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.71,0:21:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.71,0:21:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想勇於面對現實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.78,0:21:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.29,0:21:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打敗軟弱的上進心
